<td class="navbox-group" style=";background-color:#ffd068;;"><a href="/wiki/Category:Buddhist_practices" title="Category:Buddhist practices">Practices</a></td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
